Yeah!

1:36:34.221 --> 1:36:35.221
Hey!

1:36:42.963 --> 1:36:43.987
You did it!

1:36:44.098 --> 1:36:46.294
You did it, Tyson.

1:36:46.400 --> 1:36:48.027
Did you see me, Mom?

1:36:48.135 --> 1:36:50.035
Yes, honey, we saw you.

1:36:50.137 --> 1:36:52.299
