how it all works,

1:37:54.635 --> 1:37:57.570
but maybe I was first,

1:37:57.671 --> 1:38:01.938
so I could learn,
and you could learn from me.

1:42:05.419 --> 1:42:07.217
If you know so much about football,

1:42:07.321 --> 1:42:08.982
how come you don't play?

1:42:09.089 --> 1:42:12.616
