of big idiots worse than you.

1:42:13.994 --> 1:42:16.691
Whatever, dude.

1:42:16.797 --> 1:42:19.459
If it ain't Forrest Chump
comin' to take a dump.

1:42:22.803 --> 1:42:25.829
Hey, Out-of-your-mind-Stein,
you run like a girl.

1:42:25.939 --> 1:42:27.600
